      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. It has been my pride and joy and is in truly flawless condition\u2014honestly, it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken meticulous care of every single detail, so it\u2019s 100% ready for your next big adventure. It drives like an absolute dream and I promise you\u2019ll fall in love the second you see it in person. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take a look! \u2728",
