      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to let this beauty go, but it's time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014it truly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it garage-stored and sparkling clean. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. If you\u2019ve been looking for a ride that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
